  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3124481/" class="title-link">在读《四圣心源》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3124481"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/36110028/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/36110028/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">羡儿</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-03-27"
      class="main-meta">2010-03-27 17:57:15</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3124481_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  有一点医学知识是每一个敬老爱幼之人的必备，更何况在当今杂病四起，物欲横流的世界。 当年，作者因为疾病而开始学医，后成一代名医。他读懂了医界四圣的著作，学到了其中的之精髓。 作为一个外行，借着半点的古文知识读这本好书，带着拜慕珍宝的心情渴望拾到半朵或瓣的智慧之花。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3124481/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
